accessibility, and motivating progress visualization.
Dashboard Layout and Navigation
The primary dashboard displays four core sections: Learning Modules showing current/upcoming training content with progress 
bars, estimated completion time, learning objectives, and visual progress toward competency milestones; Simulation Practice
displaying available simulations, proficiency level for each simulation type, scenario progression, and latest performance results; 
Performance Metrics showing real-time accuracy/speed/quality KPIs compared to peer cohort anonymously, skill gap analysis 
