answers, supporting productive struggle and learning. Decision history and rationale tracking allow employees to review their
reasoning. Post-simulation review provides detailed feedback highlighting where decisions went well versus where improvement is 
needed.
Performance Dashboard
The Performance Dashboard provides clear visualization of individual KPIs (accuracy, cycle time, quality scores), comparative metrics 
showing peer benchmarking (anonymized), skill gap analysis identifying specific development priorities, and recommended learning 
interventions from the Performance Tracking Agent. Visual progress indicators toward 30/60/90 day proficiency targets create 
motivating milestone recognition.
Agent Interaction Panel
The right sidebar provides quick-access agent interaction: Ask Coach launches natural language queries to the Learning
Agent for personalized recommendations; Knowledge Assistant provides 24/7 question-answering and expert access.
Performance Insights show AI-generated coaching recommendations based on performance patterns; Mentor Coordination
displays mentor contact information, scheduled meetings, and talking point resources for upcoming discussions.
Visual Progress Indicators
The dashboard prominently displays proficiency progression through all four training stages: Pre-Training completion status → 
Product Training progress → Simulation Practice achievements → Continuous Development milestones. Visual badges recognize skill 
mastery, simulation scenario completions, and proficiency level achievements. Progress rings visualize movement toward 90% 
proficiency target, creating satisfying milestone recognition that drives continued engagement.
